{"tid":1394291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"公子怒屌迖哥&港豚","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:36:00.000Z","uid":148608,"like":85,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"38f76d72a58bc62c25e74de6cf0e39006cea828c","tid":1394291,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:07:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/203377069688385/posts/3506634799362579/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F203377069688385%2Fposts%2F3506634799362579%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=4fb8d0fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/203377069688385/posts/3506634799362579/</a><br />\n我宜家出街見到警察就驚。<br />\n<br />\n我前度為咗上街，同屋企人鬧翻，差啲被父母趕出街。<br />\n<br />\n有個朋友，平時見面唔多，交流唔多。然後有日我收到消息，話佢被人拉咗。<br />\n<br />\n有個觀眾睇咗我直播一年，佢保釋嗰晚，入直播度開咪，講自己點樣被人拉，邊講邊喊，喊到收唔到聲。<br />\n<br />\n近來我真係好攰，行行下街，沖緊涼，食緊飯，都會無端端流眼淚。<br />\n<br />\n然後我去動漫節，啲人話俾我知，達哥喺後台喊到收唔到，因為嗰日可能係佢最後一場活動。<br />\n<br />\n跟住又有朋友同我講，示威當日佢哋喺屋企睇直播，佢地涼住冷氣，話自己睇到好嬲。<br />\n<br />\n我屌你啦達哥！<br />\n<br />\n其實我唔憎達哥，我係嬲同失望。<br />\n<br />\n而且唔止對達哥，我係對住好多香港人嬲，亦對你地好失望！<br />\n<br />\n我宜家屌曬你地所有人呀！<br />\n<br />\n自由有代價架！<br />\n<br />\n當大家都肯一齊去分擔，個代價就會變得可以承受。<br />\n<br />\n但係，當社會上只有一小撮人肯出嚟，個代價就會顯得無比沈重。<br />\n<br />\n宜家你哋買張餐券就當贖罪券，貼下連儂牆就當做咗嘢，你地究竟知唔知咩叫革命呀？<br />\n<br />\n尤其是啲男人，屌你老母，啲婦孺都行得前過你地呀仆街！<br />\n<br />\n仲有達哥，你以為得你有包袱呀？你咁多觀眾睇你，估下嗰四十幾人入面有冇你觀眾呀？你覺得佢地又有冇包袱？<br />\n<br />\n我係引戰狗呀！但我唔覺得屌你兩句就會Shife Focus，如果一個KOL講兩句，啲人就唔記得遊行，咁政府應該出糧俾我維穩啦！<br />\n<br />\nShift Focus呢啲藉口，講出嚟，你自己都唔信啦！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n香港人已經輸唔起喇，如果再唔係街上見，咁我地最後惟有獄中再見。"},{"pid":"91f3d2e375046be0b6e456df9bbb77f5c934206c","tid":1394291,"uid":148608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:08:44.000Z","msg":"追隨大師嘅步伐！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"0fe4bf3bab83fc62402b5b0341773df6ca38e356","tid":1394291,"uid":234811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:09:49.000Z","msg":"發火屌偽善友了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75272e09593fa533d525bf609493d444cb29edf4","tid":1394291,"uid":555,"like":3,"dislike":32,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"收啦乞衣"},{"pid":"59a871875f1b689928326ddcb1b8fc604291dec1","tid":1394291,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"而家明引戰啦<br />\n迖狗仲唔快啲拍片屌鳩大師？"},{"pid":"138ca766b85a50bcdf485ef399a79bb492316a5d","tid":1394291,"uid":174403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"達狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff1fbef38b0e307a064ed23db1ed8b364cf80bf","tid":1394291,"uid":282053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"大師好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e36b1d098de554fad3109c554c47bbb0376c16d","tid":1394291,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"直線抽擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達哥：fake news"},{"pid":"a41af5dc414e3a0e57198094fe38c7d2acdc26d5","tid":1394291,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851cf083e20d6eecc31ddfbf2bda0fec8fa3aa08","tid":1394291,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"達狗今晚story又諗住點反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0a40ebdb5416d863c6cb5e3aa981d0f8eee86e","tid":1394291,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"迖狗早於上兩個月開始帶起罷工<br />\n錯怪迖狗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63c2d